# Optional: copy to `.env` to override image platform for api + frontend.
#
# Default in docker-compose: linux/amd64 — works when Docker’s Linux VM is x86_64
# (common; avoids "exec format error" on RUN steps when the host is Apple Silicon).
#
# If `docker run --rm alpine uname -m` prints aarch64 (native arm64 engine), use:
# DOCKER_PLATFORM=linux/arm64
